(4, 3, 2, '<p><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">在创作与众不同的广告语之前，有很有必要先谈我的看法:&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">在您看了几百条基本都雷同的广告语，也许已经开始产生审美疲劳，而消费者也是这样的，这也是为什么像“快到碗里来”这样不像广告语的广告语能快速流行起来，并成为人们的口头禅，因为它提供了一种很别具一格的新鲜感，所以，我们的广告语至少也要有点创意，中国的广告语经过30年的发展，消费者的审美已经提高很多并且变得刁钻起来了，像雀巢的广告语也从“味道好极了”到现在的“活出敢性”，他们也在求变，也在适应中国的消费者。</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">基于此思路，我创作的广告语:&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">1、我们只是帮您去了个皮。</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（释义: 言外之意是，我们的橙汁不添加任何东西，就是从原橙摘下来，然后制成汁到您手中，其原理类似于“我们不生产水，我们只是大自然的搬运工”。而且这句广告语采用直接和消费者对话的第一第二人称，好像面对面谈心，很有亲切感。）</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2、从原橙，到原橙汁。</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（释义:很明显的意思，同样强调原汁原味，但这种语式能让人印象深刻）</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">3、妙在妙不可言。</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（释义: 与“”味道好极了”类似，但同样运用特殊语法，为的是让大家印象深刻。）</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">4、极品橙汁，只去皮。</span></p>', 1450962382),
